    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Creators of Christian devotional images in sculpture and painting, called "retablos" and "bultos", active in Mexico from the Spanish colonial period, and later in the Spanish-speaking United States, to the present day. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
